{
  "texts": [
    "Another reason for decreased system performance is the decreasing gradients in the weight matrix.",
    "In general, this occurs as a result of the loss of features in deeper neural networks.",
    "The Residual UNet architecture aims to solve the stated problems [44].",
    "Residual is a structure of skipping connections that takes the feature map from one layer and connects it to another, deeper layer.",
    "This situation is shown in detail in Fig. 2a."
  ]
}